message.entry: The second input, numAnchors, must be a positive integer less than or equal to intmax(''uint32'').
The training input must be a datastore.
The read method of the training input datastore must return an M-by-1, M-by-2 or M-by-3 cell or table.

The bounding boxes from the read method output of the training input datastore must be an M-by-1 cell array, containing elements of N-by-4 double matrix, where N equals the number of boxes in an image.
